snippet.title: Shore of Jord – Official Announcement Teaser
snippet.description:
Shore of Jord is a story-driven cRPG set in an alternate world of Europa, where you take on the role of a retired military officer trying to resolve mysterious events from your past and survive the longest winter in history: strengthen or break friendships, find your love, and discover who you are.

General information:
🎮 Developer: TE NET
🎮 Publisher: TE NET

X: https://x.com/shoreofjord
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3176890/Shore_of_Jord/
